snippet.title: NASCAR Heat 4 Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
Only 10 days till NASCAR Heat 4 releases! 

Pre-order NASCAR Heat 4 today on your Xbox or PlayStation!
When you 'Go Gold with Gordon you'll get 3 days of early access before the competition!

Pre-Order Digitally Today: https://bit.ly/2yXoB0o

Get the latest NASCAR Heat 4 updates by following us on

Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/nascarheat

Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/nascarheat/
